# Fitness App — Project Context

## Product

健身打卡 / 热量追踪 PWA：记录运动与饮食，计算 BMR/TDEE 与当日热量缺口，打卡墙与社区动态。主要用户为家庭成员小规模使用。

## Stack

- **Frontend**: Vite 8, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind 4, vite-plugin-pwa — `src/`
- **Backend**: Node.js Express (ESM), `server/src/`
- **DB**: PostgreSQL 16 — local Homebrew; production Docker in `deploy/`
- **Deploy**: `scripts/deploy-tencent.sh` (manual)

## Key paths

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/pages/`, `src/components/`, `src/lib/` | React UI and client logic |
| `server/src/index.js` | API routes |
| `server/migrations/*.sql` | Schema (run in filename order) |
| `deploy/` | docker-compose + nginx for production |
| `docs/README.md` | Doc hub — start here for humans and Cursor |
| `docs/GETTING-START.md` | Local dev setup |
| `docs/ai-playbook.md` | Cursor agent checklist |
| `docs/milestones/` | Per-feature specs (`_TEMPLATE.md`) |
| `docs/requirements/` | GitHub Issue intake |
| `docs/ops/` | DB, deploy, PWA ops guides |
| `docs/architecture/` | Overview, API contract, deploy |
| `scripts/verify-local.sh` | Local quality gate before push |
| `scripts/new-feature.sh` | Start `feat/<slug>` branch + milestone skeleton |

## Local dev

- DB: `brew services start postgresql@16`, database `fitness` — see `docs/ops/本地数据库启停.md`
- API: `cd server && npm run dev` (port 3001)
- Web: `npm run dev` (port 5173), `.env.local` with `VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001`

